{"tid":2451604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（多謝傍聽師 送車師） 理大暴動案 官拒五人保釋","createTime":"2021-03-18T08:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T08:34:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e019fe998f9ef0f09968ada504a9d789b7f0d50b","tid":2451604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/HM6O2OW4OBDCDP6JZPGYTO37SY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FHM6O2OW4OBDCDP6JZPGYTO37SY%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2XhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=050c7f3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FHM6O2OW4OBDCDP6JZPGYTO37SY%2F&h=36e2bb33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/HM6O2OW4OBDCDP6JZPGYTO37SY/</a><br />\n<br />\n（多謝傍聽師 送車師）<br />\n 理大暴動案 官拒五人保釋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7YqMP-igXYiq3Divt5rFuQvfypU=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JBATCZAM7ZCI5K5OOXR4Y4CHOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7YqMP-igXYiq3Divt5rFuQvfypU%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJBATCZAM7ZCI5K5OOXR4Y4CHOI.jpg&h=ad385034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■五名被告昨在九龍城裁判法院提堂後由囚車押走，大批聲援者奔跑送別。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科日前拘捕四男一女，指五人涉嫌串謀其他人參與前年11月理工大學內發生的暴動事件。五名被告昨被押解到九龍城裁判法院提堂，包括四名學生，全部控以一項串謀暴動罪，控方表明案件將轉交區域法院審理，並反對各人保釋。裁判官鄭念慈考慮後，拒絕全數五人的保釋申請，全部還柙看管，以等候轉介區院的文件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件轉介區院<br />\n<br />\n五人依次為。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官聽畢辯方申請後，以案情嚴重為由拒絕五人的保釋申請，案件押後至4月7日再提訊。理大圍城一役，警方近月先後起訴29人在校園內或附近參與暴動，案件已轉介區院，29人最終共15人須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC826/21<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LRpNRmGwl2IHITrSsdhf6RSZXU8=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WQXBNWWZNRGTTH3VJ4VWZYKGOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLRpNRmGwl2IHITrSsdhf6RSZXU8%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWQXBNWWZNRGTTH3VJ4VWZYKGOA.jpg&h=1750a146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前年理大圍城多日，校內多人其後被控告暴動罪。"},{"pid":"970e033b0dcf4feb30c29ca58d6a47e1fcfb7987","tid":2451604,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7518071cd1d27f3fc580319dc3f05a68d7eff6a8","tid":2451604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7YqMP-igXYiq3Divt5rFuQvfypU=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JBATCZAM7ZCI5K5OOXR4Y4CHOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7YqMP-igXYiq3Divt5rFuQvfypU%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJBATCZAM7ZCI5K5OOXR4Y4CHOI.jpg&h=ad385034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■五名被告昨在九龍城裁判法院提堂後由囚車押走，大批聲援者奔跑送別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas